Cozy living room with a separate kitchen that opens to a spacious light-filled and vaulted great room. Easy access to the yard with sliding glass doors and a large entertainment deck. Outside enjoy an expansive yard, dog run, chicken coop, sunny garden spaces and extra parking for RV or boat storage.
